Biology and fertility life table of Eriopis connexa, Harmonia axyridis and Olla 
v-nigrum (Coleoptera: Coccinellidae).

Zazycki LC(1), Semedo RE(2), Silva A(2), Bisognin AZ(2), Bernardi O(1), Garcia 
